data.description: Welcome to 714 Raleigh Creek on a corner lot within the Meadowbrook Place Subdivision. Offering 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, and 2078 sq. ft. Nestled in a special neighborhood and close to I-75, this home offers the peaceful balance of privacy and convenience. Roof, siding, doors and windows in 2022, flooring in 2019, and high efficiency furnace/AC in 2023. Enjoy the in-ground pool and 12x28 shed nearby. With these stunning features and is move in ready, this property is truly a must see. Don't miss the chance of making this house your home. Schedule a viewing today!
